          Generated magnetic and kinetic energy fields, zonal flows, and entropy
          levels of early Earth using supercomputers and parallel computing.
        </p>

        <p>
          Successfully implemented and validated a radial electrical conductivity
          profile with a sharp gradient at the coreâ€“mantle boundary, bridging
          idealized models with realistic planetary bodies.
        </p>

        <p>
          Conducted extensive test cases analyzing magnetic surfaces, tilt,
          zonal flows, and kinetic/magnetic field behavior for poster
          presentation.
